text: Ljungarum Church () is a church in the town of Jönköping in Sweden. It belongs to Jönköping Christina-Ljungarum Parish of the Church of Sweden. The building dates back to the 13th century. == References == ==Other websites== Category:Church of Sweden churches Category:Buildings and structures in Jönköping Category:13th-century buildings and structures
title: Ljungarum Church
